@startuml
actor User
collections WebApp Server
database Database

User -> WebApp Server : Enter user data
WebApp Server -> WebApp Server : checks if passwords comply with requirements
alt passwords comply
  WebApp Server -> Database : checks for duplicate account
  alt no duplicate
    Database --> WebApp Server : send conformation
    WebApp Server -> Database : makes new Database entry
    WebApp Server -> User: displays confirmation message
  else duplicate found
    Database --> WebApp Server : sends error message
    WebApp Server -> User : displays error message
  end
else passwords don't comply
  WebApp Server -> User : displays error message and clears passwords
end

@enduml
